##  MARKETPLACE & ECONOMIC FUNCTIONS
53. **Function of creating product listings** — Post items or services for sale.
54. **Function of searching products** — Browse by keyword, category, or location.
55. **Function of buying and selling** — Secure transactions between users.
56. **Function of adding to cart** — Temporarily store items before checkout.
57. **Function of processing payments** — Use M-Pesa, crypto, or cards for payment.
58. **Function of rating sellers and buyers** — Leave reviews after transactions.
59. **Function of managing orders** — Track purchase and delivery status.
60. **Function of reporting fraudulent listings** — Protect users from scams.
61. **Function of promoting listings** — Paid boosts for product visibility.
---
##  EVENTS & COMMUNITY FUNCTIONS
62. **Function of creating events** — Add event details, posters, and dates.
63. **Function of RSVPing or joining events** — Attend and share interest.
64. **Function of hosting live sessions** — Stream webinars or community meetups.
65. **Function of buying tickets** — Purchase access to premium or live events.
66. **Function of sharing event links** — Promote via invites or QR codes.
67. **Function of creating fundraisers** — Raise money for school or charity projects.
68. **Function of donating to causes** — Send money to verified campaigns.
