##  MONETIZATION & BUSINESS FUNCTIONS
69. **Function of running ads** — Promote pages, events, or marketplace listings.
70. **Function of managing ad budget** — Control spending and targeting.
71. **Function of viewing ad analytics** — Check impressions, clicks, and engagement.
72. **Function of receiving revenue** — Earnings from ads, sales, or donations.
73. **Function of withdrawing money** — Transfer funds to M-Pesa or crypto wallets.
74. **Function of subscribing to premium** — Access exclusive or ad-free experiences.
