##  AI, RECOMMENDATION & PERSONALIZATION FUNCTIONS
75. **Function of recommending friends** — Suggests potential connections intelligently.
76. **Function of recommending content** — Feeds personalized posts or materials.
77. **Function of recommending study topics** — Suggests relevant notes or lessons.
78. **Function of detecting spam or harmful content** — Uses AI moderation.
79. **Function of summarizing conversations** — AI summarizes chats or study notes.
80. **Function of chat with AI bot** — Conversational help for study or social questions.
