##  ADMINISTRATION & SECURITY FUNCTIONS
81. **Function of verifying reports** — Admin reviews reported content.
82. **Function of banning or suspending users** — Restricts violators or spammers.
83. **Function of managing announcements** — Broadcast updates or maintenance alerts.
84. **Function of viewing analytics dashboard** — Overview of user activity, traffic, and engagement.
85. **Function of reviewing verification requests** — Confirms authenticity of users or pages.
86. **Function of managing categories & tags** — Controls discoverability and structure.
87. **Function of moderating content** — Approves, removes, or flags inappropriate material.
---
##  SYSTEM, SETTINGS & MISC FUNCTIONS
88. **Function of switching language or theme** — Changes interface language or dark/light mode.
89. **Function of enabling offline mode** — Access cached content without internet.
90. **Function of syncing PWA data** — Keeps app data updated across devices.
91. **Function of push notifications** — Sends real-time alerts for events or messages.
92. **Function of managing cookies & privacy consent** — Ensures legal compliance.
93. **Function of contacting support** — Chat or email help desk.
94. **Function of bug tracking** — Logs errors for developers.
95. **Function of session management** — Detects and terminates suspicious logins.
